text: "Little Black Submarines" is a 2012 song by The Black Keys and is the fourth single from their seventh studio album El Camino. It went to number 54 in Canada, number 12 in Belgium, number 77 in the Netherlands and number 6 on the Billboard Hot Rock & Alternative Songs charts.
